res1 = residuals(mod1)
fit1 = predict(mod1)
# Diagnostic Plot 1: Residuals versus fitted values
plot(fit1, res1, xlab = "Fitted Values", ylab = "Residuals", cex = 0.8)
abline(h = 0)

res2 = residuals(mod2)
fit2 = predict(mod2)
# Diagnostic Plot 1: Residuals versus fitted values
